#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/proto.rst:2
msgid "内网常用协议"
msgstr "Common Internal Network Protocols"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/proto.rst:4
msgid "Windows查询名称解析的顺序为DNS、mDNS、LLMNR、NBNS。"
msgstr "The Windows name resolution query order is DNS, mDNS, LLMNR, and NBNS."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/proto.rst:7
msgid "NetBIOS"
msgstr "NetBIOS"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/proto.rst:8
msgid ""
"NetBIOS（Network Basic Input/Output System）是基于网络的交互协议，通常使用UDP 137、UDP "
"138、TCP 139等端口。Windows在安装TCP/IP协议时会默认启用该协议，可能导致未设置权限校验的网络资源被访问。"
msgstr "NetBIOS (Network Basic Input/Output System) is a network-based interaction protocol that commonly uses ports such as UDP 137, UDP 138, and TCP 139. Windows enables this protocol by default when the TCP/IP protocol is installed, which may allow access to network resources that do not have permission checks configured."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/proto.rst:10
msgid ""
"基于NetBIOS有NBNS (NetBIOS Name Service)服务，通常监听在UDP "
"137端口，该服务提供三种功能：将NetBIOS名称解析到IP、查询某一个NetBIOS节点的状态，注册/释放一个NetBIOS名。"
msgstr "NBNS (NetBIOS Name Service) is based on NetBIOS and usually listens on UDP 137. It provides three functions: resolving NetBIOS names to IP addresses, querying the status of a NetBIOS node, and registering or releasing a NetBIOS name."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/proto.rst:12
msgid "可以使用 ``nbtstat`` 工具利用NetBIOS协议管理网络。"
msgstr "The ``nbtstat`` tool can be used to manage networks through the NetBIOS protocol."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/proto.rst:15
msgid "LLMNR"
msgstr "LLMNR"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/proto.rst:16
msgid ""
"链路本地多播名称解析 (Link-Local Multicast Name Resolution, "
"LLMNR)是一个基于DNS数据包格式的协议，IPv4和IPv6的主机可以通过此协议对同一本地链路上的主机执行名称解析。该协议在Windows "
"Vista后被引入。 LLMNR监听UDP 5355端口，可以通过多播地址 224.0.0.252 (或 "
"``FF02:0:0:0:0:0:1:3``) 访问。"
msgstr "Link-Local Multicast Name Resolution (LLMNR) is a protocol based on the DNS packet format. IPv4 and IPv6 hosts can use it to perform name resolution for hosts on the same local link. This protocol was introduced after Windows Vista. LLMNR listens on UDP 5355 and can be reached through the multicast address 224.0.0.252 or ``FF02:0:0:0:0:0:1:3``."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/proto.rst:20
msgid "mDNS"
msgstr "mDNS"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/proto.rst:21
msgid ""
"mDNS (multicast DNS) 在Windows 10中被引入，监听UDP 5353端口，对应的多播地址为 224.0.0.251 ( "
"``FF02::FB`` ) 。mDNS主要实现了在没有传统DNS服务器的情况下使局域网内的主机实现相互发现和通信。"
msgstr "mDNS (multicast DNS) was introduced in Windows 10 and listens on UDP 5353. The corresponding multicast address is 224.0.0.251 (``FF02::FB``). mDNS mainly enables hosts on a LAN to discover and communicate with each other when no traditional DNS server is available."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/proto.rst:24
msgid "WPAD"
msgstr "WPAD"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/proto.rst:25
msgid ""
"网络代理自动发现协议 (Web Proxy Auto-Discovery, WPAD) "
"是一种客户端使用DHCP和/或DNS发现方法来定位一个配置文件URL的方法。在检测和下载配置文件后，它可以执行配置文件以测定特定URL应使用的代理。"
msgstr "Web Proxy Auto-Discovery (WPAD) is a method for clients to use DHCP and/or DNS discovery to locate a configuration file URL. After detecting and downloading the configuration file, the client can execute it to determine which proxy should be used for a specific URL."
